title: Spain: Catalan independence protesters burn Spanish flags and portraits of King Felipe
description:
Protesters burnt Spanish flags and portraits of Felipe VI, during a Catalan independence protest organised by the left-wing Popular Unity Candidacy party in Barcelona, Sunday.
